136
00:09:48,254 --> 00:09:49,554
It's come!

137
00:09:49,554 --> 00:09:51,254
The Sleeping Kogoro!

138
00:09:51,254 --> 00:09:54,954
Now that Mr. Mouri's taken that pose.

139
00:09:54,954 --> 00:09:57,654
