140
00:09:57,654 --> 00:09:59,854
The truth of the locked room murder

141
00:09:59,854 --> 00:10:02,581
that was committed in room B.

142
00:10:02,581 --> 00:10:04,154
Who are you?

143
00:10:04,154 --> 00:10:06,354
Oh, I'm sorry,

144
00:10:06,354 --> 00:10:10,054
I'm Mr. Mouri's number one disciple, Amuro.

145
00:10:10,054 --> 00:10:13,054
Ai's not there?

146
00:10:13,054 --> 00:10:14,354
No.

147
00:10:14,354 --> 00:10:17,754
I looked in the restrooms of the cars nearby too, but...

148
00:10:20,254 --> 00:10:23,054
Oh, it's mail from Ai.

149
00:10:23,054 --> 00:10:26,354
I'm okay so don't worry about me.

150
00:10:26,354 --> 00:10:27,954
