A great problem.

178
00:11:42,854 --> 00:11:44,683
A chain lock is usually made

179
00:11:44,683 --> 00:11:46,685
so that even if a hand were to be inserted

180
00:11:46,685 --> 00:11:48,687
between the door from outside,

181
00:11:48,854 --> 00:11:50,689
